T1  - Understanding and Tackling Societal Grand Challenges through Management Research
AU  - George, Gerard
AU  - Howard-Grenville, Jennifer
AU  - Joshi, Aparna
AU  - Tihanyi, Laszlo
Y1  - 2016/09/30
